    "Furthermore, conversational AI, which is a type of GenAI, might have a personal purpose.",
    "Conversational AI is defined as a computer system capable 'of engaging in natural language conversations with humans' (Jaspet.ai chat, n.d.).",
    "This use is considered to be for entertainment purposes (McKinsey & Company, 2023).",
    "However, as already mentioned, behind the arousal of simply chatting with AI, conversational AI has as well economic purposes and it is not risk-free (El Atillah, 2023).",
    "Finally, there might as well be a purely scientific and educational use of GenAIthe academic purpose."
